## Specific Rules for Current Project

1. Use `pnpm` as the package manager.
2. Use `Tanstack Start` as the base full-stack framework.
3. Use `Jotai` as the state management library.
4. When adding shadcn components, use the `@basecn` registry by default, e.g. `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add @basecn/button`